title: Cherry-POP: A Humorous - Girl in Control Erotic Story
description: What would you do for Ten Million Dollars? Who would you do it with? What if it was fun to do? Cherry has an opportunity if she can just grab the brass ring. Something or rather someone is trying to rain on her parade. Maybe she just needs to take charge of the situation and do what needs to be done to keep her dream on track. But that doesn't mean the solution cant be fun for her too, right?
author: Cally Morehead
